      <title>法国寻求到 2035 年将化石燃料发电量削减至 40%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-06/france-to-seek-cut-in-fossil-fuel-generation-to-40-by-2035</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国能源转型部长艾格尼丝·潘尼尔-鲁纳切尔 (Agnes Pannier-Runacher) 在接受《La Tribune Dimanche》采访时表示，法国的目标是到 2035 年将化石燃料在其能源消费结构中的比例从 60% 以上减少到 40%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-06/france-to-seek-cut-in-fossil-fuel-generation-to-40-by-2035</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国核心通胀放缓增强了美联储的乐观情绪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-06/world-economy-latest-easing-us-core-inflation-seen-reinforcing-fed-optimism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着 2023 年接近尾声，美国潜在的价格压力可能会继续消退，这支撑了美联储对通胀路径的乐观态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-06/world-economy-latest-easing-us-core-inflation-seen-reinforcing-fed-optimism</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普希望维持 21% 的企业税，并扩大个人减税范围</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-06/trump-considers-making-2017-personal-tax-cuts-permanent</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，唐纳德·特朗普计划永久实施他担任总统时制定的 2017 年个人减税政策，同时保持企业税水平不变，以吸引工薪阶层和中产阶级选民，如果他重新入主白宫的话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-06/trump-considers-making-2017-personal-tax-cuts-permanent</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 18:49:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将于三月初发表国情咨文</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-06/biden-invited-to-give-state-of-the-union-speech-in-early-march</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统将于 3 月 7 日向国会发表国情咨文演讲，这个日期相对较晚，将在“超级星期二”初选以及 2024 年初国会就联邦资金问题展开的任何摊牌之后发表。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-06/biden-invited-to-give-state-of-the-union-speech-in-early-march</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 15:49:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普选票被清除反映了自由党资助团体的努力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-06/trump-ballot-removals-reflect-efforts-of-liberal-funded-groups</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普退出科罗拉多州和缅因州的初选标志着两个主要由自由派捐助者资助的激进团体的胜利，这两个团体有条不紊地将有关第十四修正案的学术思想实验转变为现实世界的法律策略。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-06/trump-ballot-removals-reflect-efforts-of-liberal-funded-groups</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 14:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾称中国气球威胁国际飞行安全</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-06/taiwan-says-china-balloons-threaten-international-flight-safety</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾国防部谴责中国多次向海峡两岸发射气球，并敦促北京立即停止。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-06/taiwan-says-china-balloons-threaten-international-flight-safety</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 14:28:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伦敦警察厅调查邮局欺诈丑闻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-06/metropolitan-police-investigating-post-office-for-fraud-after-horizon-scandal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国警方正在调查与一桩丑闻相关的潜在欺诈行为，在该丑闻中，数百名邮局经理被错误地指控盗窃和虚假会计。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-06/metropolitan-police-investigating-post-office-for-fraud-after-horizon-scandal</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 14:24:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布林肯表示土耳其已准备好在以色列与哈马斯战争中发挥积极作用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-06/blinken-meets-turkey-s-erdogan-as-middle-east-tensions-rise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯在外交之旅开始时与土耳其领导人进行了交谈，旨在避免中东发生更广泛的战争，并争取阿拉伯国家对加沙冲突后治理的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-06/blinken-meets-turkey-s-erdogan-as-middle-east-tensions-rise</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 12:27:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>克里米亚空军基地遭到袭击后，俄罗斯顿涅茨克空袭造成十人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-06/ukraine-says-it-destroys-russian-post-at-saky-air-base-in-crimea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基辅表示，俄罗斯在克里米亚西部的一个军事指挥所被摧毁数小时后，俄罗斯对乌克兰东部城镇波克罗夫斯克发动空袭，造成至少十人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-06/ukraine-says-it-destroys-russian-post-at-saky-air-base-in-crimea</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 08:22:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国失落的一年已经过去，但 2024 年可能不会好多少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-06/germany-s-lost-year-is-over-but-2024-may-not-be-much-better</link>
      <description><![CDATA[即使德国经济最终在 2024 年开始再次扩张，它也很难摆脱一代人以来最疲软的年度表现之一背后的恐惧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-06/germany-s-lost-year-is-over-but-2024-may-not-be-much-better</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
